{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they kept their clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the plan was, if there's a round-up, and the-- and the Slovakians are rounding up the Jews, they'll see the other apartment had a padlock.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they'll think, well, no one outside a padlock-- you can't-- you know, it was a good excuse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they'll-- the family will go into hiding, into that apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one of them will give himself up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He'll open the door, will tell them, I'm the only one here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The rest of the family is away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My uncle was the one that stayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My grand-uncle was the one that stayed in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The rest of the family- his wife, his daughter, his grandson, and his two sons, and daughter-in-law, and, I believe, three other children, went into the other apartment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they closed-- they sealed this apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my great-uncle was taken to camp, and, I guess, gassed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the rest of the family stayed a couple of days in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then they went out, and they stayed in hiding with the Croatian ambassador, in his residence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Who was-- well, I don't know how he became the Croatian resident, but they must've been-- he must've paid him off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were-- they were in hiding until after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So technically, had I stayed with my grand-uncle, or my father, conceivably, unless they would have said, well, you go with your grand-uncle.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- that farmer told us, he says, there's no way you'll get him to-- to take you to Hungary, no matter how much money you would pay.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we have a friend-- I have a friend who is a pharmaceutical student at the University of Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
